N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 47.9 - Alterations not deemed substantial

State Regulations

Applications for alterations other than substantial
alterations shall be made in the same manner as prescribed for substantial
alterations except that no fee need accompany the same. Notes
